    GenerateTopResearcherNews ..> NewsRepository : calls
    GenerateTopResearcherNews ..> HIndexCalculator : calls

    %% Application Course → repos/services
    EnrollInCourse ..> UserRepository : calls
    EnrollInCourse ..> CourseRepository : calls
    EnrollInCourse ..> EnrollmentService : calls
    EnrollInCourse ..> LogRepository : calls
    DropCourse ..> UserRepository : calls
    DropCourse ..> CourseRepository : calls
    DropCourse ..> LogRepository : calls
    RecordMarks ..> UserRepository : calls
    RecordMarks ..> CourseRepository : calls
    RecordMarks ..> LogRepository : calls
    AssignTeacher ..> UserRepository : calls
    AssignTeacher ..> CourseRepository : calls
    CreateCourse ..> CourseRepository : calls
    CreateCourse ..> IdSequence : calls
    CreateCourse ..> LogRepository : calls
    SetCourseCapacity ..> CourseRepository : calls
    SetCoursePrerequisite ..> CourseRepository : calls
    AddLesson ..> CourseRepository : calls
    AddLesson ..> RoomScheduler : calls
    ViewTranscript ..> UserRepository : calls
    ViewTranscript ..> CourseRepository : calls
    ViewTranscript ..> GpaCalculator : calls

    %% Application Library
    BorrowBook ..> BookRepository : calls
    BorrowBook ..> UserRepository : calls
    BorrowBook ..> LogRepository : calls
    ReturnBook ..> BookRepository : calls
    ReturnBook ..> LogRepository : calls
    AddBook ..> BookRepository : calls
